(My instinct would be to go with the following to avoid rocking the boat when it comes to seed corpus naming etc, but I'm too new to this aspect of fuzzing to carry much weight).
```C++
void base58_encode_decode(FuzzBufferType buffer);
void base58check_encode_decode(FuzzBufferType buffer);
void base32_encode_decode(FuzzBufferType buffer);
void base64_encode_decode(FuzzBufferType buffer);
void psbt_base64_decode(FuzzBufferType buffer);

FUZZ_TARGET(base_encode_decode)
{
    base58_encode_decode(buffer);
    base58check_encode_decode(buffer);
    base32_encode_decode(buffer);
    base64_encode_decode(buffer);
    psbt_base64_decode(buffer);
}
```

